# API Technologies

1. REST - Representational State Transfer
2. GraphQL - Graph Query Language
3. RPC - Remote Procedure Call

- REST is easy to debug right from Networks in browser devtools
- REST is prone to underfetching or overfetching

- GQL caching is much more comple
- GQL uses its own Schema Defenition Language SDL

- gRPC uses Protocol Buffers binary format for communication, highly performant
- Interfaces are defined as IDL
- No browser support
